annotations: Professional Summary: I’m a hard worker, genuinely with a diligent work ethic. I’m a great communicator. I am motivated, determined, respectful, humble, and moreover always willing to do the best job. Multitasking is a great asset of mine. Providing excellent customer service, organization, categorization, management and accurate cashiering are a few tasks I juggle. Exceeding expectations I set for myself is what drives me. Exuding professionalism, a positive attitude and striving to prosper in the work place is ultimately my professional goal.

I currently work as a sales associate. I inventory new items received. I ensure all material is free of defects. I confirm the quantitative and description of each item is correct. I censor all merchandise prior to sale. I am responsible for arranging, organizing, ticketing, and labeling various items. I solely maintain and manage the shoe department, ensuring items are categorized by the right size and group throughout the day. I interact with customers to address inquiries/concerns and provide immediate resolutions to help solve discrepancies. Recently I’ve expanded my work ability and knowledge by assisting with cashiering and helping in other departments.
High School: El Haynes Public Charter HS 2011-2016
